HEADWORD: Apogean
<hw>Ap`o*ge"an</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Connected with
the apogee; <as>as, <ex>apogean</ex> (neap) tides, which occur when the
moon has passed her apogee</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

